Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.07,0:22:44.09,ED sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}Nedotýkaš sa ma
Dialogue: 1,0:22:44.55,0:22:48.55,ED sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}Moje srdce, je ako mesiac
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.55,0:22:53.18,ED sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}Neustále sa mení
